Package: RTemplate
Type: Package
Title: Template R Package for Reproducible Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Template", family = "Author", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "template@example.com")
  )
Description: Example package that wraps a simple Boston housing data
    analysis pipeline (cleaning, modeling, and plotting) into a single
    function `make_figures()` for demonstration of reproducible and
    automated workflows.
